Name: Swallow the Sea
About the game: Take a short surreal swim. Swallow the Sea is a 8-15 minute 2D survival exploration game featuring eat and grow combat and multiple areas. You are a lowly egg cell on a journey through a swollen sea of strange and humanoid fish. Prey on smaller life and growing larger and stronger to perhaps someday be born.
